    <h4><b>Strawberry Oatmeal</b></h4>
      
      <div class="text-left">
<p class="title"><b>INGREDIENTS:</b></p>
<p class="title">1 Serving</p>
   <p>
      <li>4 Tbsp oats</li>
      <li>1 Cup (250 ml) milk</li>
      <li>1 Tsp honey</li>
      <li>1/4 Medium boiled beets (Pinky trick!)</li>
      <li>4 Strawberries</li>
      <li>1 Kiwi</li>
      <li>2 Plums</li>
      <li>1 Tbsp chia seeds</li>
      <li>1/2 Tbsp germinated wheat seed juice dessert</li>
      <li>5 Raw almonds</li>
  </p>
